original: Lindgren, Oscar Emanuel, stadsveterinär, Karlshamn, f. 2/11/85 i Jämshög, Blek. L, av grosshandl. Elof L. o. Ulrika Hultstein. G. 27 m. Svea Wallander. Barn: Ulrika f. 28, Elisabeth 33. — Mog:ex. i Kristianstad 05, vet:ex. 11. Besiktn:vet. i Gbg 12-15, dito i Karlshamn sed. 15, stadsvet. där sed. 17, besiktn :vet. v. kontrollslakt, nr 104 i Mörruni sed. 27, besiktn :vet, v. Mörrums köttbesiktn :byrå sed. 31. Led. av Karlshamns hälsov:nd sed. 21. , ’’Lindgren, Bror Ossian Gaetano. riksbanksdirektör, Växjö, f. 31/7/83 i Skön, Västernorrl. 1, av insp. J. T. L. 0. Marie Loui’se Flodberg. G. m. Vi-van Hjelm. — Stud:ex. 03. Anst. i riksb. i Umeå 03, ord. bokh. i Luleå 11, registr. i Växjö 14, förste bokh. i Kalm. 18, kassör i Umeå 21, kamr. i Växjö 27, i Norrköp. 36, dir. i Växjö sed. 40. Siffergransk. v. Småi. Ensk. Bank i Kaim. 19-21, skattm. v. Umeå elem:lärov. f. fl. 23-27, sekr. i Västerb. 1. sinnes-slöanst. 26-27, stat. rev. h. Kronob. 1. hush :sällsk. egnah :nd 31-36, 11. Kronob. 1. hush :’sällsk. 33-36, ordf. i tax:ndn i ett par ilandskomm. 33-34, led. av styr. f. Riksbankstj :m. fören. 30-42, v. ordf. 39-42. Hobby: ornitologi. RVO.
translated: Lindgren, Oscar Emanuel, city veterinarian, Karlshamn, b. 2/11/85 in Jämshög, Blekinge, son of merchant Elof L. and Ulrika Hultstein. Married on 27th with Svea Wallander. Children: Ulrika born in 28, Elisabeth in 33. — M.A. in Kristianstad in 05, veterinary degree in 11. Veterinary examiner in Gothenburg from 12 to 15, also in Karlshamn from 15, city veterinarian there from 17, veterinary examiner for control slaughter, number 104 in Mörrum from 27, veterinary examiner at Mörrum's meat inspection office from 31. Member of Karlshamn's health board from 21. ’’Lindgren, Bror Ossian Gaetano, director of the Central Bank, Växjö, b. 31/7/83 in Skön, Västernorrland. Son of inspector J.T.L. and Marie Louise Flodberg. Married to Vivian Hjelm. — High school graduate in 03. Employed at the Central Bank in Umeå in 03, regular accountant in Luleå in 11, registered in Växjö in 14, head accountant in Kalmar in 18, treasurer in Umeå in 21, auditor in Växjö in 27, in Norrköping in 36, director in Växjö from 40. Number checker at Smål. Ensk. Bank in Kalmar from 19 to 21, treasurer at Umeå elementary school and others from 23 to 27, secretary at Västerbotten's mental institution from 26 to 27, state revenue officer at Kronoby household society's estate from 31 to 36, district revenue officer at Kronoby household society from 33 to 36, chairman of the tax board in a couple of rural municipalities from 33 to 34, member of the board for the Central Bank Staff Association from 30 to 42, vice chairman from 39 to 42. Hobby: ornithology. Knight of The Royal Order of Vasa.
